Migrating From CRM Analytics Licenses Purchased Before 10/20/2015 to New CRM Analytics Platform Licenses

To complete migration from previous Analytics Cloud Builder and Analytics Cloud Explorer licenses purchased before October 20, 2015, to the new CRM Analytics Growth license, you may need to set up CRM Analytics users in your organization with new permission sets.

Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

When Salesforce provisions your organization with the new CRM Analytics Growth license, you may have to set up some users with the new license.

Analytics Cloud Builder license users: no additional setup required.
Analytics Cloud Explorer license users: remove the old license and assign the new CRM Analytics Growth license instead.

If users require a new setup, follow the steps in CRM Analytics Platform Setup. Assign them the new permission set license, create one or more new permission sets, and assign the permission sets to users.
title: Migrating CRM Analytics Licenses
